Date: Wed, 22 Jul 2026 06:12:36 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Clip surface content to rounded pane corners

Single-pane content uses window radius; splits keep
concentric R-w. SwiftUI clipShape + compositingGroup
and AppKit masksToBounds on the surface host.
